section:
Hundred-headed hydras arise from the sea on all sides. Hissing
venomously, they lash out to seize men from the decks.

	
	
	
;
add 2 if your crew quality is excellent, add 1 if it is good, and subtract 2 if it is poor.

	
		Everyone is killed; 
	
	
		You alone survive; 
	
	
		Many losses;
		reduce Crew Quality to poor
		and 
	
	
		The hydras are driven off;
